---
title: One-Pot Turkey & White Bean Chili Verde with Sour Cream
description: Get ready for a flavor explosion, courtesy of tonight’s riff on a classic chili verde. Upgrading the usual green chile and tomatillo stew, our chefs added Southwest-spiced turkey and hearty cannellini beans to the mix. They topped it all off with a dollop of sour cream and green salsa, because everything about your chili verde should be both slurpable and dippable. Prepare yourself for a big ol’ spoonful of deliciousness.
